_sText:
Creates a random path from the CT spawn to the Terrorist spawn.

Notes: The metal grate can only be shot through with powerful enough weapons; I stuck the spawns a little close, so getting stuck in the back might be a problem if there are AFK'ers, or people slow at buying (you should be able to jump them); nightvision goggles help in the shadowy areas, and help you see through the glass (x-ray goggles?)
